org.sopra.api.model

Interface Edge<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - The type of node used in the graph.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FlowEdge<V>, PowerLine, ResidualEdge<V>

    public interface Edge<V>
    The egde of a graph. Edges connect two nodes, so this edge type has two getters for the nodes connected by it, getStart and getEnd. It also has a weight. In scenario graphs, the weight is the capacity.
